      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基于区块链的同行评审流程。核心角色有作者、区块链平台，还有两位评审员。作者先提交数据对象，区块链负责分配评审任务，最后汇总决策。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Author",
        "Blockchain",
        "Reviewer 1",
        "Reviewer 2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。作者和两位评审员我都用actor表示，区块链作为participant。作者提交的数据对象具体包含哪些字段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Author",
        "Blockchain",
        "Reviewer 1",
        "Reviewer 2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "数据对象需要三个字段：instruction指令、response回复内容、source来源信息。另外区块链有个内部动作是pick reviewers，从池子里随机选两位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "data object",
        "instruction",
        "response",
        "source",
        "pick reviewers"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出作者到区块链的数据提交，加上三个字段。然后画区块链自循环的选评审员动作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Author",
        "Blockchain",
        "data object",
        "pick reviewers"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "评审员投票这块要仔细一点。Reviewer 1和Reviewer 2各自独立向区块链提交commit vote，有五种可选状态：accept接受、reject拒绝、feedback需要修改、refer转交、skip弃权。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reviewer 1",
        "Reviewer 2",
        "commit vote",
        "accept",
        "reject",
        "feedback",
        "refer",
        "skip"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，两位评审员是并行向区块链提交投票，不是互相通信对吧？而且五种投票状态都要列在消息里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reviewer 1",
        "Reviewer 2",
        "Blockchain",
        "commit vote"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，都是直接写给区块链，彼此看不到对方的票。五种状态都写上，用OR连接。最后区块链根据两人投票做最终decision决策。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reviewer 1",
